<Legal
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Exploreans Watamu Beach Club & Villas."
>
  <p><em>Last updated: May 2026</em></p>

  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
  <p>Exploreans Watamu Beach Club & Villas ("we", "us", "our") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or make a reservation.</p>

  <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Personal identification:</strong> name, email address, phone number, passport details</li>
    <li><strong>Booking information:</strong> arrival/departure dates, room preferences, special requests</li>
    <li><strong>Payment data:</strong> processed securely through our payment providers — we do not store card details</li>
    <li><strong>Technical data:</strong> IP address, browser type, device information, cookies</li>
    <li><strong>Communication records:</strong> emails, messages, and feedback you send us</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>We use your personal data to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Process and confirm your reservations</li>
    <li>Communicate about your stay (pre-arrival, during, post-departure)</li>
    <li>Provide customer support and respond to enquiries</li>
    <li>Improve our services and website experience</li>
    <li>Send promotional communications (only with your consent)</li>
    <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
  <p>We process your personal data based on:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Contractual necessity:</strong> to fulfil your booking</li>
    <li><strong>Legitimate interests:</strong> to improve our services and prevent fraud</li>
    <li><strong>Legal obligation:</strong> to comply with applicable laws</li>
    <li><strong>Consent:</strong> for marketing communications (which you can withdraw anytime)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share it with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Planhotel Hospitality Group (our parent company) for operational purposes</li>
    <li>Payment processors and booking engine providers</li>
    <li>Service providers (airport transfers, excursion operators) — only when necessary for your stay</li>
    <li>Legal authorities when required by law</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>We retain your personal data for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes outlined in this policy, or as required by law. Booking records are typically retained for 7 years for accounting and tax purposes.</p>

  <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>Under applicable data protection laws, you have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
    <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
    <li>Request deletion of your data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
    <li>Object to or restrict certain processing activities</li>
    <li>Request data portability</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent for marketing at any time</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>8. Cookies</h2>
  <p>We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your browsing experience. For detailed information, please see our <a href="/cookies">Cookie Policy</a>.</p>

  <h2>9. Security</h2>
  <p>We implement appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect your personal data against unauthorised access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.</p>

  <h2>10. International Transfers</h2>
  <p>As part of the Planhotel Hospitality Group based in Switzerland, your data may be transferred to and processed in Switzerland and other countries. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place for such transfers.</p>

  <h2>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available on this page with the updated date.</p>

  <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>For any questions about this privacy policy or to exercise your rights, please contact us:</p>
  <p>
    <strong>Exploreans Watamu Beach Club & Villas</strong><br>
    c/o Planhotel Hospitality Group<br>
    Via Nassa 17, 6900 Lugano, Switzerland<br>
    Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@planhotel.com">privacy@planhotel.com</a>
  </p>
</Legal>
